Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:18.47,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:28.44,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:33.54,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:38.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:51.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, singing those chords of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:01:00.82,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:05.66,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:11.33,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:20.63,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:33.13,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:57.96,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:01.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.19,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:25.28,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:34.06,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:38.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:40.29,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:44.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:45.84,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:51.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.27,0:23:51.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:57.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:57.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:03.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:09.49,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:14.44,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:40.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Helvetian witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A Helvetian soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I? Am I a hostage of the Helvetians?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have taken me as a hosta-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:31.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Infantry of the Roman Empire, First Tank Division. Thirteenth Tank Battalion, Company B, {\i1}Feldwebel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:36.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah Aldora. Identification Number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:43.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Infantry of the Roman Empire, {\i1}Feldwebel{\i0}, A'ishah Aldora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:49.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Identification number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:19.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so I actually made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:08.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I need energy to escape, that's why I'm eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:30.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, have any of you seen the bones of the angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you don't understand anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:47.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that such trumpets still existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May I try?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A great trumpet... That I'm able to see something like th-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:10.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:30.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:37.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I serve the Helvetian Orthodox Church.\NMay the blessings of all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of those heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:45.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one god. Such a greeting is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:01.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't talk, it will cause a lot of trouble for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:08.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel the least bit thankful, then you should talk honestly with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to talk about my mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:26.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wanted to see the bones of the angel that's supposedly in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:41.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother, she was in this fortress, in this stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:48.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was taken prisoner on the Eastern front, where she met my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:54.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a child, she often told me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:04.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to see it, the angel my grandmother had seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:09.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel of Apocalypse that had brought divine retribution upon the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:44.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël? Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:49.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the Invisible Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:56.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this snow is so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:01.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And headquarters sending us on a patrol? On a day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:07.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up on Madame Jacquotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:10.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:17.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. Just keep looking and looking and then you can say "maybe" when you just can't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:27.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that you were kind of like Rio for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:44.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the cliff, eleven o'clock. About 400 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up. Can you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her clothes are all frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata. Take her coat off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're switching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:31.40,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}The Visitor - A Snowy Field Ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:48.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore operations at a facility like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:52.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are the greatest genius in the history of the Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can win with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe this to you, Miss Noël Kannagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:15.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They found her during their patrol. A Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like her left leg is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fingers are turning black!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:32.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Frostbite. If we don't work fast, she may lose those fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she saved her fingers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:08.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She put everything she had into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:13.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like she was repairing the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:15.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be a scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would expect to see a Roman soldier in a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:40.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that. This is the first time I've seen a Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:48.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls them the enemy and everything, so I thought they would look more evil or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:53.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Romans might think the same way about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:06:02.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw her, I thought that maybe the Romans were just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, what are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, it's about time. The Recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:20.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace conferences still aren't going smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to report this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:31.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, she'll be taken to the capital and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:40.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about that! She stepped into enemy territory at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier must be prepared for torture-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:43.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will decide how we handle her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some time, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:00.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When you carried her here, did anyone see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I was focused on bringing her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Rio. What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roman. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:02.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely nothing! She doesn't understand Helvetian at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:07.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All we've figured out is her identification number and that her name is A'ishah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:13.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann. I am in command here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:20.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some nice breasts you have. Just what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I sucked and massaged them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I play with your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:32.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she really doesn't understand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:42.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem. It means we can't interrogate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find someone who speaks Roman quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:48.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:55.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can interrogate her and file a report, we will hold her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we might test our luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, it's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:09.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah, welcome to the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Time-Telling Fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:30.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:35.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be saying it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:19.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata's always like that, but why is Noël acting like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Atonement, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Engel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have studied Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. If we could talk to her, maybe-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:55.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yumina. Got enough hands to shovel snow at the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:13:00.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The children are working very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:06.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,People grow every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the sound of Miss Kanata's trumpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio would say she still has a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:23.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Didn't you head over to Treize to stock up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Things happen. Ended up being a wasted trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like things aren't going your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:35.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me. I've been hearing some ugly rumors about the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:55.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Rio would let you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! This is absolutely wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:29.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya's sound echoed in me, it echoed in Rio,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:34.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the same piece echoed in both Helvetia and Rome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound will echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether in Rome or Helvetia, it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporary repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Danke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "Danke" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It means "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:24.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:37.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This town never saw the lions mouth, but parents, siblings, and relatives included, everyone's lost someone they knew in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the nicest people, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:46.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the owner of the distillery, Mikhail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:52.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had some business with him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:57.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Helvetian army's on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:07.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If that has anything to do with this Roman soldier you've got here, then we've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we have to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:19.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi, do you know anyone who knows Roman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a light greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:52.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any of that! Ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she wants to see the bones of the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bones of the angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother was a soldier at the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was captured on the Eastern front and met her grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, she often told me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon brought the world to ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't care. Just tell us what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:25.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see the Angel of the Apocalypse that brought divine retribution upon the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She says that's why she came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A call to march?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This code is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:40.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First Royal Guard Battalion, Ninth Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:44.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth? Isn't that Colonel Hopkins'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They call him the Demon of Binnenland.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:56.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he revived ancient weapons and wiped out three whole towns in a single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:04.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He doesn't know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:09.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, you don't have much time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:13.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You girls need to figure out what to do, and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to hand her over, or-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:17.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:20.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Helvetian soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we failed this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't make it in time, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:32.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio said she didn't want anyone else to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:35.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she would do everything she could!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she went!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all a part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:52.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The following is an order from the Commander of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:20:00.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This order is my own decision. I will take full responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:04.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you all understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:18.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon 1121 Commander, Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:22.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Several days ago, a Roman scout was captured in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:28.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, due to an accident during interrogation, we were unable to confirm several details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:34.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately following, we heard reports of Roman forces in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:49.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, command of Fortress 1121 has been transferred to the Ninth Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start shouting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:07.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah just told me about the legend of the Maidens of the Fire, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different. According to her-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a complete search!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:16.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:20.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a guard at every gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She says that she still doesn't know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A rat, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:05.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fortress 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:32.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A large contingent of Roman forces has appeared on the border between Seize and Nomansland?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:25.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Echo Through the Blue Sky
